Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.63,0:00:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戌时已到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉马上要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.14,0:00:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了找齐四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.91,0:00:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了用这把铁碎牙打败奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.54,0:00:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了寻找突然失踪的奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.38,0:00:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一行人展开漫长的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家曾经一起\N度过好多次难关
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.41,0:00:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这次大家又要一起\N面对心灵的地狱了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师加上珊瑚\N七宝跟云母
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿梭于时空\N发生在战国时代与现代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:25.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:32.15,OP,,0,0,0,,分散在蓝蓝天空上的 七颗星星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:36.86,OP,,0,0,0,,每一颗星星 都刻着我的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.17,0:00:40.77,OP,,0,0,0,,就算梦想被粉碎 我也要寻找爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.07,0:00:44.80,OP,,0,0,0,,我无处可逃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:48.87,OP,,0,0,0,,紧紧抓着我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:57.30,OP,,0,0,0,,那些骗人的光阴 我再也不会输给它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:02.67,OP,,0,0,0,,睁大眼睛 看清楚这瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.67,0:01:06.85,OP,,0,0,0,,它仍然紧紧围绕着我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:10.85,OP,,0,0,0,,让人啜泣的 现实生活中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.85,0:01:14.85,OP,,0,0,0,,最重要的…到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:18.72,OP,,0,0,0,,繁忙的这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:22.95,OP,,0,0,0,,永恒的碎片 忽隐又忽现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:26.87,OP,,0,0,0,,去触摸 去捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:33.80,OP,,0,0,0,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:39.03,OP,,0,0,0,,为了得到最后的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:46.27,OP,,0,0,0,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:01.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.93,0:02:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样啊  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在还找不到出口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别吵了  会分心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.43,0:02:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一早到现在都还没搞定\N马上就要天黑了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛抖个不停啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.01,0:02:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师\N这座森林果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.51,0:02:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  不会错了\N一定是妖怪的巢穴…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  又爆胎了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种没用的废物  扔掉算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.16,0:02:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我妈买给我的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一股邪恶的气息…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.17,0:02:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座森林的主人\N差不多该现身了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会出现的会是鬼  还是蛇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪快点现身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么话快说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在那边装模作样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点给我滚出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临我这座可悲的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第100话 真实的恶梦\N可悲的森林之役
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这个家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.78,0:03:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  你看这妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,0:03:39.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  是蛾天丸同类
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦?你们认得\N蛾天丸那家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是我们族人的耻辱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.82,0:03:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说他跟一些\N低贱的人类狼狈为奸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后居然死在半妖的手里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这把刀还真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.47,0:03:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚说的半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时那样的结果\N我还正觉得无趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会有妖怪血的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这只死妖虫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想帮蛾天丸报仇的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天本大爷\N会很兴奋的奉陪到底
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮蛾天丸报仇?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别说笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种邪魔歪道  死了活该
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会理他那些闲事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爱怎么说都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你们这些飞蛾死虫怪\N也一样没有好感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是什么呀\N啊  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太…太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直冲进身体里面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力气…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.14,0:05:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渐渐被吸走…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.64,0:05:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.95,0:05:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连铁碎牙也不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.08,0:05:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会吃人类的鲜血的\N是那些邪魔歪道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们全族的人\N一向吃的都是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐惧的心\N还有脆弱的灵魂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒  别被控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂!弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.91,0:05:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要坚强一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在再大声都没用  臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们根本就听不见你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用等到天亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:05:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那些分身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:06:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会把他们的\N灵魂跟肉体吃个精光了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤…试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子只有打败这个妖怪\N才能解开法术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在连续不断的恶梦中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.79,0:06:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些隐藏在内心深处的\N恐惧跟绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.86,0:06:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都给我唤醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  云母
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要紧吧  琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子连云母都比不过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.26,0:07:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看他应该还不能应付实战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒不这么认为  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得琥珀\N耍链条耍得很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你这么说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一琥珀有什么危险\N还有我跟着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  我好害怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.10,0:07:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事了  姐姐在这…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愉快  愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样  弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样出来散散心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那些什么痛苦烦恼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就都把它忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦心师父
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么没有看见\N我爸爸在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦心师父?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你亲生父亲告诉我\N恐怕要跟你来世再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来世再见…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时候恐怕已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.36,0:08:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸…爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  爸爸\N我捡了这么多松果回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.34,0:09:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么啦  草太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.43,0:09:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蚋在里面耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有点怪怪的\N我觉得很不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么啊  草太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股瘴气是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.95,0:09:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能  怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草太  你快跑  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草太  振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么声音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万不可以过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.18,0:10:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续受苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受完苦之后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有永无止尽的绝望\N等着你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.42,0:10:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好地 慢慢地\N品尝那些恐怖的滋味吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死妖怪\N你到底对他们做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过让他们做做梦而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们做梦?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管人也好 妖怪也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隐藏在内心深处的那种恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:43.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会借着梦境\N变得非常非常的具体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这些东西\N就是我们的饵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这死妖怪简直乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在立刻放了戈薇他们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  你这只半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看得出来\N你开始感到恐惧了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.53,0:11:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不跟大家成群结队的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.36,0:11:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本是胆小又没用的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算剩下我一个\N我也照样能打
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然拿我的同伴当成你的饵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不能忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在那边逞英雄了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最害怕最难忍受的恐惧\N我也会一并吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你还能威风多久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招吧  风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呸  光会用一张嘴说说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为这样就算赢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:11:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:11:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我这条命没了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些不断帮我\N啃食他们的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有肉体的分身\N全都会复活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.09,0:12:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候就是你的死期了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等着成为\N你那些同伴的饵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.93,0:12:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而到那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.10,0:12:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也才有机会\N真正摆脱孤独的恐惧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.61,0:12:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虫茧居然没有消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可恶了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个浑蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.59,0:13:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于办到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个人打败妖怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打败妖怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次爸爸一定会\N夸奖我做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐…姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.81,0:14:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是姐姐你的错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.31,0:14:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你没有夸奖我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦心师父  放了我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那个风穴\N现在已经用到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后你哪里都去不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.72,0:14:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.93,0:14:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定把奈落找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只差一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师  你怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别…别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.81,0:14:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们全都不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.09,0:14:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么会…\N我根本没打开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.36,0:15:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师\N你就那么想帮我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了帮我\N牺牲同伴的性命也在所不惜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切全部都是你的杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你对我爷爷\N下了这个风穴诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.79,0:15:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜啊  救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.89,0:15:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在上课的时候做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么啦  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很少看到你上课打瞌睡耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚睡得还真熟哩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是因为太过用功念书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是因为这种事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:15:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续待在这里会有危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.93,0:16:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞刃血爪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的韧性跑到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然会被梦境给侵蚀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是这么脆弱的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.82,0:16:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的看错你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.36,0:16:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你就这样放弃自己的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就要一个人\N自己去击败奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.57,0:16:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候你可不要\N跟在后面哭哭啼啼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.21,0:16:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不可以\N让那只飞蛾怪吃掉你的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一向都不是那么柔弱的女子\N不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.93,0:17:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快醒来命令我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.50,0:17:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命令我坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  原谅姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.34,0:17:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这一辈子恐怕都没有机会\N回到我身边了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先杀了你\N然后跟你一起死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了从奈落手中把你抢回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这个办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你绝对不能杀了琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要活着把他带回来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会给大家添麻烦而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.87,0:17:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要再咯里罗唆的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正大家在一起就是比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:17:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你也满会打架的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙到底在怕什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.82,0:18:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再打开风穴的话\N我会先折断你这只手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要等到打败奈落\N风穴才能收起来对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是裹足不前的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的一点都没错  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.57,0:18:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定要撑下去  七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狐火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  看不出来\N你真有两下子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.32,0:18:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:18:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…身上好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时候在说什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在人类的样子\N打不过他的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会扔下你一个人跑掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.85,0:19:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊  还有犬夜叉在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要还有犬夜叉在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.87,0:19:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那帮好朋友在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有再大的困难\N我们一定都能一起克服的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.39,0:19:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.86,0:19:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:20:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样才是我认识的你们嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.17,0:20:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在马上可以\N离开这座森林了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出口就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:15.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.03,0:20:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森林不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为刚刚的一切\N都是蛾罗丸的幻术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害得我们无缘无故\N耽误了行程
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.64,0:20:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有我在一旁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们根本就软弱到不行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么  有什么不满吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:20:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实  你说的并没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只限今天随便让你说说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么说是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就好了嘛  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.36,0:21:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都认同你够厉害\N不就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  这样我不接受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们真的认为\N是我救了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.44,0:21:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好歹跟我\N说一声“谢谢”才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样  戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就麻烦你\N代表大家说一句话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.25,0:21:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.65,0:21:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咿呀…你想干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒来命令我坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.29,0:21:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.39,0:21:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.76,0:21:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢  谢  你  哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.70,0:21:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.47,0:21:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是过来叫我坐下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也该继续上路咯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  我肚子饿了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  戈薇\N刚刚你跟我说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.21,0:21:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说一次啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.11,0:21:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又没关系  再说一次嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.91,0:21:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你烦不烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.11,0:22:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  喂  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.75,0:22:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  我在叫你耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.12,0:22:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦好啦  给我坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:37.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.50,0:22:15.15,ED,,0,0,0,,红红的太阳照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.72,0:22:24.95,ED,,0,0,0,,也照遍过去和现在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.10,0:22:34.22,ED,,0,0,0,,那些夕阳下的想象
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:44.22,ED,,0,0,0,,这颗心真的能承担吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.75,0:22:49.20,ED,,0,0,0,,告诉我什么办法才能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.50,0:22:54.12,ED,,0,0,0,,活得比以前更开朗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.12,0:23:01.52,ED,,0,0,0,,这么做就算会让自己委屈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:08.07,ED,,0,0,0,,要默默承受伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:12.25,ED,,0,0,0,,会失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.65,0:23:19.50,ED,,0,0,0,,真正的歌仍会不断在我心中回荡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.95,0:23:29.52,ED,,0,0,0,,真正的歌才是我的路标
